g.text: 2. View photos/videos posted by users the current user follows, in newsfeed.
6. Search for users using name, handle.
1. Highly available: User should have something on the newsfeed.
2. Eventually consistent: Acceptable if posts take time to show up in feed.
3. Latency: Low latency to generate feed.
4. Durability: No uploaded content should get lost.
5. Scalability: Should scale to support millions of reads and writes.
6. Reliability: able to handle s/w and h/w failures.
50 million photos, 30 million videos per day.
3MB max size of photos, 150MB max size of videos.
Maximum storage cost from photos and videos. Can ignore metadata cost for now.
